# Persian RTL Configuration

## Language Requirements

- All English content should be translated to Persian
- HTML lang attribute must be set to `fa-IR`
- There is no LTR layout - everything is RTL only
- Maintain RTL support with proper spacing and layout adjustments

## RTL Layout Guidelines

- Design components with RTL-first approach
- Ensure proper text alignment for Persian content
- Handle RTL-specific spacing and margin adjustments
- Test all UI components in RTL context
- Consider Persian text length differences when designing layouts

## Content Translation

- Translate all user-facing text to Persian
- Maintain semantic meaning in translations
- Consider cultural context in translations
- Ensure proper Persian typography and spacing